Fujikura to Develop Fuel Cell for Civil Aircraft With Boeing

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-03-02T02:27:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/japan-s-fujikura-plans-to-develop-fuel-cell-for-civil-aircraft-with-boeing.html
  Fujikura Ltd . said it plans to
develop a fuel cell for civil aircraft with  Boeing Co . The
Japanese company expects commercial use by 2015, according to a
statement on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
